      "side": 1,
      "message": "spent a lot of time above in merge dicts, but this is better place to stick my comment.\nBasically, i\u0027m uneasy with what you chose, it\u0027s as if i wish there were 2 consts:\n\nkUseDefault (\u003d\u003d\u003d current None value)\nkDelDefault\n\nbut OTH, my proposal is complicated and maybe never used, and perhaps can be added later. Right? Was this your thinking, too?",
